# Kiserian Main SDA Church Website - Modular Architecture Rules

## Module Isolation
- Modules access only their own database tables
- Cross-module communication via documented APIs only
- No direct SQL joins across module tables
- API format: {success, data/error, message}

## Code Organization
- Backend: controllers/{module}.controller.js, routes/{module}.routes.js
- Frontend: contexts/{Module}Context.jsx, pages/{module}/, components/{module}/

## Dependency Rules
- AUTH ← ALL, SETTINGS → ALL
- TELEGRAM → CONTENT, GALLERY
- DEPT → TREASURY, CONTENT, DOC, SMS, APPROVAL
- TREASURY → APPROVAL, PAYMENT, SMS
- PAYMENT, SMS, DOC, GALLERY → APPROVAL → NOTIF
- No circular dependencies

## Testing
- Unit tests: __tests__/{module}.test.js
- Integration: __tests__/integration/{module}.test.js
- E2E: __tests__/e2e/{workflow}.test.js

## Code Review Checklist
- No direct cross-module table access
- All inter-module communication uses APIs
- New endpoints documented
- Tests cover changes
- No circular dependencies

